# Force LF regardless of the checking-out machine's core.autocrlf. Without
# this, a Windows checkout with autocrlf=true rewrites every text file to
# CRLF, which gofmt then flags as unformatted (gofmt only emits/accepts LF)
# even though no actual code changed — see CLAUDE.md's `gofmt -l .` rule.
* text=auto eol=lf
